WebFeed is a simple yet privacy-focused RSS/Atom feed reader. 

WebFeed could detect feeds in web pages automatically. If user subscribe it, WebFeed would check new articles repeatedly and show the new badge when available. And user could read the new feed summaries in a single feed stream.

All code are open sourced under the MIT license.

https://github.com/taoso/webfeed
